  "text": "The Five Facet Mindfulness Questionnaire-Short Form (FFMQ-SF) assesses different aspects of mindfulness [CITATION_1] . The FFMQ-SF is a 24-item short form of the Five Facet Mindfulness Questionnaire, a comprehensive measure for assessing mindfulness [CITATION_2] . The FFMQ-SF has demonstrated reliability and validity as well as sensitivity to change in samples of adults with anxiety and depression as well as fibromyalgia [CITATION_3] .",
